dc:description: Pale blue glass.  Intact.  Material fair.  Pinprick bubbles.  Frosting, milky weathering and iridescence.  Golden brown areas.  Three small red marks on neck which may be paint or polish which was dripped on at a later date.  Toilet bottle, lacrimatory type.  Unworked rim outsplayed.  Cylindrical neck with a slight constriction at its base.  Drop-shaped body.  Slightly concave base.
Gazda: Toilet bottle. Glass, free blown.
